"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-news-uk-liverpool-katarina-johnsonthompson-belgian-paris-olympics-b1175829.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"News|UK  Katarina Johnson-Thompsonhas described her love forLiverpooland how the city gave her a \\\"never-give-up attitude\\\", after winning her first Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 238, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"score\": 0.9916925742149805, \"rank\": 0.006852848271285659, \"text\": \"Katarina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katarina_Waters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Liverpudlian took silver in the heptathlon on Friday inParis, coming second toBelgianrival Nafissatou Thiam.\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"score\": 0.9999945848218169, \"rank\": 5.4152074264428744e-06, \"text\": \"Liverpudlian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\"}, {\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafissatou_Thiam\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafissatou Thiam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafissatou_Thiam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafissatou_Thiam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson, 31, on Saturday spoke about her love for Liverpool and how it shaped her as a person.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 565, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999976641902, \"rank\": 2.3341948566003174e-09, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I love the people of Liverpool and I love what they stand for and that shapes my character, of that never-give-up attitude, and that underdog attitude and yes, it means the world  Katarina Johnson-Thompson  She said: \\\"Liverpool is my home, it always is my home even if I train and live elsewhere.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999976641902, \"rank\": 2.3341948566003174e-09, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999976641902, \"rank\": 2.3341948566003174e-09, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I love the people of Liverpool and I love what they stand for and that shapes my character, of that never-give-up attitude, and that underdog attitude and yes, it means the world.\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999976641902, \"rank\": 2.3341948566003174e-09, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started my career at Liverpool Harriers and I am indebted to them as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999976641902, \"rank\": 2.3341948566003174e-09, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson said the silver medal was \\\"a long time coming\\\".\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels incredible that you know we got one over the line.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's been a long time coming, it's been a very short cycle but it's my fourthOlympicsand I am really happy to add that medal to my collection,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson said: \\\"I have got absolutely no regrets.\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried my absolute best and my best on that day was second place by about 30 points, so you know I was very close to an Olympic gold medal and to me that's just validated our team's belief that it was possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if there were times she doubted she would get there, she said: \\\"I have had doubts all the time, every athlete I feel like, even if they do not admit it, always has doubts - crippling doubts, but luckily I have got a team around me that has the belief in me that I sometimes do not have in myself, and that leads me to do great things and I am so grateful to them.\\\"\", \"from\": 1725, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about her plans for the future, she said: \\\"I feel like as long as I am competitive I will continue to do heptathlon.\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really happy that I am able to put together my heptathlon in a different way now and it's given me such longevity in the sport.\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am really really excited for the next couple of years.\\\"\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 3276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2458, \"end\": 2467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9254338665587827, \"rank\": 0.07573